        "subtitle": "How Terence Reilly turned a 110 year old brand into the Birkin bag of water bottles. And what it actually teaches us about modern marketing.",
        "category": "Mainstream",
        "date": "April 15, 2026",
        "author": "The Margin",
        "read_time": "5 min",
        "cover_image": "https://i.pinimg.com/736x/78/b5/54/78b554c8d5be5e453915bca885e4a9e7.jpg",
